PUT http://localhost:3000/api/categories/1 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "asd"
}


###

#Exclusão de uma categoria
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/categories HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

